---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@components/container.astro";
---

<Layout title="Vote for the Best Manuscript Award 2026">
  <Container>
    <div class="mt-16">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm mb-3">
        <span class="text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">Best Manuscript Award 2026</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight lg:leading-tight max-w-3xl">
        Vote for the Best Manuscript Award 2026
      </h1>
      <hr class="border-slate-200 mt-10" />
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 items-start gap-8 lg:gap-16 mt-10">
      <div>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
          It's time to vote for the best manuscript in the field of metaproteomics!
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600 mt-4">
          Following the call for the best manuscript of the year, we have received a number of manuscripts.
          All manuscripts have now been evaluated by our scientific committee, who have selected the three
          finalists. Now it's up to you, the metaproteomics community, to vote for your favorite.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Finalists</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mb-4">Please find here the finalists' manuscripts (order according to submission date):</p>
        <ol class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-black text-white text-sm font-semibold shrink-0">1</span>
            <span class="text-slate-800">Hellwig et al.</span>
            <a href="/images/best_manuscript_award_2026/Manuscript1_Hellwig.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">(PDF)</a>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-black text-white text-sm font-semibold shrink-0">2</span>
            <span class="text-slate-800">Hinzke et al.</span>
            <a href="/images/best_manuscript_award_2026/Manuscript2_Hinzke.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">(PDF)</a>
            <a href="/images/best_manuscript_award_2026/Manuscript2_Supplementary.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">(Supplementary)</a>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-black text-white text-sm font-semibold shrink-0">3</span>
            <span class="text-slate-800">Malliet et al.</span>
            <a href="/images/best_manuscript_award_2026/Manuscript3_VanDenBossche.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">(PDF)</a>
          </li>
        </ol>

        <div class="mt-8 border-l-4 border-blue-400 bg-blue-50 rounded-r-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm text-slate-700">
          <p class="mb-2">
            <strong>Please note</strong> that each member has only one vote and that only members of the
            Metaproteomics Initiative can vote. The voting system will be open until
            <strong>May 6, 2026, 12:00 noon (CET)</strong>.
          </p>
          <p>
            Not yet a member?
            <a
              href="https://forms.gle/zAqJDPZNvf7vSoNi9"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-semibold">
              Sign up
            </a>
            and secure your chance to vote for the Best Manuscript.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-slate-500">
          If you have any questions or problems, please contact us at
          <a href="mailto:info@metaproteomics.org" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">
            info@metaproteomics.org
          </a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Cast your vote</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mb-2">
          Ready to vote? Use the form below to select your favorite manuscript. You will need to be a
          Metaproteomics Initiative member to participate.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mb-6">
          Voting closes on <span class="font-semibold text-slate-800">May 6, 2026 at 12:00 noon (CET)</span>.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://forms.office.com/pages/responsepage.aspx?id=3hyB1-_sbEmPkaF4YkG5nE9OcrFOgI9AjPOBs9GtvKZUMk1VOVhHQVZGMEZIVjFFQ1RTT1NGUk42My4u&route=shorturl"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-black text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors">
          Go to the voting form
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-200">
      <a href="/" class="text-sm text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-800 transition-colors">
        &larr; Back to homepage
      </a>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
